  4668                                  ;       Routine:        ConTakeToken
  4669                                  ;
  4670                                  ;       Description:    This routine extracts the next token from the given source buffer.
  4671                                  ;
  4672                                  ;       In:             DS:EDX  source buffer address
  4673                                  ;                       DS:EBX  target buffer address
  4674                                  ;
  4675                                  ;       Out:            DS:EDX  source buffer address
  4676                                  ;                       DS:EBX  target buffer address
  4677                                  ;
  4678                                  ;       Command Form:   Line    = *3( *SP 1*ALNUM )
  4679                                  ;
  4680                                  ;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
